OL,3,CLabour has not learned lessons of
OL,4,Cdefeat in Scotland ` SNP Westminster
OL,5,Cleader
OL,7,FLabour has not "learnt the lessons of
OL,8,Fits election defeat" in Scotland the
OL,9,Fnew SNP Westminster leader has said as
OL,10,Funcertainty in Downing Street
OL,11,Fcontinues.
OL,13,FSNP MP Dave Doogan has called for the
OL,14,FUK Government to bring forward an
OL,15,Femergency cost-of-living budget to
OL,16,Fhelp families instead of being "stuck
OL,17,Fin paralysis".
OL,26,@oD@POUpD@TO]xD@`OUyD@MO]
