OL,3,CLabour has not learned lessons of
OL,4,Cdefeat in Scotland ` SNP Westminster
OL,5,Cleader
OL,7,FHe is calling on the Chancellor to
OL,8,Fannounce an emergency budget this
OL,9,Fmonth to deliver an urgent package of
OL,10,Ffinancial support including removing
OL,11,FVAT on fuel until the crisis is over,
OL,12,Fscrapping the Labour Government's fuel
OL,13,Fduty hike, and introducing a household
OL,14,Fenergy price cap.
OL,16,FMr Doogan said: "This week of
OL,17,FWestminster chaos has shown the Labour
OL,18,FGovernment hasn't learnt the lessons
OL,19,Fof its election defeat and is
OL,20,Frepeating the same mistakes that saw
OL,21,Fit hammered at the polls.
OL,26,@xD@QOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
