OL,3,CLabour has not learned lessons of
OL,4,Cdefeat in Scotland ` SNP Westminster
OL,5,Cleader
OL,7,F"It's not all about Keir Starmer and
OL,8,Frearranging the deck chairs at
OL,9,FWestminster.
OL,11,F"People voted for real change ` but
OL,12,Fnone has been forthcoming. They voted
OL,13,Ffor urgent action on the cost of
OL,14,Fliving emergency ` but the Labour
OL,15,FGovernment is stuck in paralysis and
OL,16,Fhasn't announced a single measure to
OL,17,Fhelp.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
