OL,3,CLabour has not learned lessons of
OL,4,Cdefeat in Scotland ` SNP Westminster
OL,5,Cleader
OL,7,F"Instead, they are only talking about
OL,8,Fthemselves ` squabbling over who gets
OL,9,Fto be leader, while they plunge the UK
OL,10,Finto another crisis of their own
OL,11,Fmaking.
OL,13,F"This has been going on for two years
OL,14,Fnow. The Labour Government has spent
OL,15,Fmore time talking about whether Keir
OL,16,FStarmer can survive than anything
OL,17,Felse."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUyD@FO]
