OL,3,CLabour has not learned lessons of
OL,4,Cdefeat in Scotland ` SNP Westminster
OL,5,Cleader
OL,7,FHis comments come amid the rising
OL,8,Funcertainty at Westminster with
OL,9,Fgrowing calls for the Prime Minister
OL,10,Fto resign, with Wes Streeting having
OL,11,Fresigned as health secretary on
OL,12,FThursday.
OL,14,FMr Doogan continued that, while he
OL,15,Fagreed the UK Government should
OL,16,F"settle this crisis", he said that
OL,17,Fpeople around the country are not
OL,18,Finterested in Labour infighting.
OL,26,@xD@AOUxD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
