OL,3,CLabour has not learned lessons of
OL,4,Cdefeat in Scotland ` SNP Westminster
OL,5,Cleader
OL,7,FHe said: "Yes, we need to break this
OL,8,Fimpasse and settle this crisis ` but
OL,9,Fpeople aren't interested in whether
OL,10,FWes Streeting or Andy Burnham get to
OL,11,Ffurther their own careers, they want
OL,12,Furgent help with soaring bills and a
OL,13,Fbetter future from the terminal
OL,14,Fdecline of Broken Brexit Britain.
OL,26,@oD@JOU
