OL,3,CLabour has not learned lessons of
OL,4,Cdefeat in Scotland ` SNP Westminster
OL,5,Cleader
OL,7,F"The UK Government must bring forward
OL,8,Fan emergency cost-of-living budget
OL,9,Fthis month to help households with
OL,10,Freal financial support ` removing VAT
OL,11,Fon fuel, scrapping the fuel duty hike,
OL,12,Fand introducing a Household Energy
OL,13,FPrice Cap to reduce bills by hundreds
OL,14,Fof pounds.
OL,16,F"Every day it fails to act, and
OL,17,Ffocuses on itself, Westminster is
OL,18,Fshowing people in Scotland why they
OL,19,Fneed the fresh start of independence
OL,20,Fto lower bills and build a better
OL,21,Ffuture."
